WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.260
Guys, we have missed the deadline.

00:00:03.220 --> 00:00:05.700
The client is demanding a release immediately.

00:00:06.580 --> 00:00:08.020
We don't have a lot of time.

00:00:08.260 --> 00:00:11.180
Let's just get the launch page live and see about the rest later.

00:00:12.660 --> 00:00:14.060
And what about engineering?

00:00:14.760 --> 00:00:17.320
We need to validate the core tracking first.

00:00:18.040 --> 00:00:20.780
Alex, what do you think we should prioritize?
